data.title: Lucy Liu ‘Kill Bill’ Signed 8x10 Photo ‘O-Ren Ishii’ ACOA
data.meta_description:
Own a piece of cinematic history with this stunning 8x10 photo signed by Lucy Liu, who played the iconic character O-Ren Ishii in the film 'Kill Bill.' This is a genuine, original autograph certified by AutographCOA (ACOA), ensuring its authenticity for any collector or fan.


This item is perfect for any entertainment or film memorabilia collection. Don't miss out on the chance to own a piece of movie history signed by one of its most memorable stars. Add this signed Lucy Liu 8x10 photo to your collection today. Signed in person in 2024. Guaranteed authentic autograph certified by ACOA authentication
